  Select Model and Effort
  Access legacy models by running codey -m <model_name> or in your config.toml

  1. gpt-5.2-codex (default)  Official model from OpenAI provider.
  2. gpt-5.2                  Official model from OpenAI provider.
  3. gpt-5.1-codex-max        Official model from OpenAI provider.
  4. gpt-5.1-codex-mini       Official model from OpenAI provider.
